  "description": "<p>A low-profile, versatile harness for all-round rock climbing and gym routes, the Ophir 3 is designed for all-day comfort and breathability. 2-part webbing in the waistbelt distributes the load over the entire width of the belt, while 2-layer foam construction provides comfort and stability for working routes or at hanging belays.</p><ul><li>Self-locking buckles on the waist and legs for safety and ease of use</li><li>Lower tie-in point has a protector to prevent abrasion and add good safety margins</li><li>Tie-in point and belay loop wear indicators show red threads when excessively worn</li><li>Adjustable leg loops with drop seat for ease of use while wearing layers or crampons</li></ul>",
